data.value: How to Enter Transactions: Enter the Transaction Date, Amount, Type and a short Description. Click on "Confirm" to add the Transaction or "Cancel" to Cancel the Transaction. How to Export/Open: Click the "Save" Icon to Export to a XML File or the "Open" Icon to Open from a XML File. Click the "Export" icon to Export to a PDF File. Click the ""Balance" icon to balance your checkbook.
